---
title: Bison Arais Platter with Roasted Sweet Potato and Hummus Sauce
description: Bison makes a statement here in our new Middle Eastern-inspired platter. Arais is a smoky-spiced meat-stuffed flatbread that may just be a new staple in your recipe collection! Served alongside a fresh salad, roasted sweet potato and all topped off with a delightful honey lemon hummus sauce – your taste buds are going to thank us!
